   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Complete the steps as described in <xref href="../mapping-fields_143887215_143887215/143887215.xml"
                     format="dita">Mapping Fields</xref>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Before saving a field mapping, change the value of the <uicontrol>Custom Format</uicontrol> field to <uicontrol>Yes</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Add appended text to the field <uicontrol>Custom Field Value</uicontrol>. Text should be added in the following format: "appendedText1<uicontrol>{value}</uicontrol>appendText2". During sync <uicontrol>{value}</uicontrol> is replaced by the actual field value in the destination application. For example, to append a URL to the value of the field, you might specify the custom field value as something like "https://yourdomain.my.salesforce.com/<uicontrol>{value}</uicontrol>/abc".</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
